<figureCitation box="[950,1032,1447,1473]" captionStart="FIGURES 1 – 10" captionStartId="6.[264,382,1596,1620]" captionTargetBox="[294,1317,313,1573]" captionTargetId="figure@6.[267,1351,303,1603]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="FIGURES 1 – 10. Microthereva argentiventris. 1. Antenna. 2. Tergite 8, epandrium, cerci, hypoproct, dorsal view. 3. Sternite 8, gonocoxite, ventral view. 4. Gonocoxite, dorsal view. 5. Gonocoxite, lateral view. 6. Gonostylus, lateral view. 7. Aedeagus, dorsal view. 8. Aedeagus, ventral view. 9. Aedeagus, lateral view. 10. Female internal reproductive organs. Scale = 0.1 mm. Abbreviations: C = cercus, CD = common duct, DA = dorsal apodeme, Dp = distiphallus, EA = ejaculatory apodeme, Epa = epandrium, F = furca, Gs = gonostylus, Gx = gonocoxite, H = hypandrium, Hpt = hypoproct, Igp = inner gonocoxal process, Sp = spermatheca, Spd = spermathecal duct, SpS = spermathecal sac, SS = sensory seta, S 8 sternite 8, T 8 = tergite 8, VA = ventral apodeme, VL = ventral lobe." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/173536/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Figs. 4</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation box="[1044,1074,1447,1473]" captionStart="FIGURES 11 – 19" captionStartId="10.[264,382,1265,1289]" captionTargetBox="[287,1298,328,1233]" captionTargetId="figure@10.[256,1332,300,1242]" captionTargetPageId="10" captionText="FIGURES 11 – 19. Microthereva variventris. 11. Tergite 8, epandrium, cerci, hypoproct, dorsal view. 12. Sternite 8, gonocoxite, ventral view. 13. Gonocoxite, dorsal view. 14. Gonocoxite, lateral view. 15. Gonostylus, lateral view. 16. Aedeagus, dorsal view. 17. Aedeagus, ventral view. 18. Aedeagus, lateral view. 19. Female internal reproductive organs. Scale = 0.1 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/173537/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">13</figureCitation>
